00:19:35.675 --> 00:19:36.885 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA]
Mm.

00:19:49.606 --> 00:19:52.317 position:50% align:center
--[FROG KEMONO growl]
--[AKIRA screams]

00:19:55.820 --> 00:19:58.782 position:50% align:center
Okay. Um. What exactly
am I suppose to do?

00:19:58.865 --> 00:20:00.075 position:50% align:center
[shouts]

00:20:01.117 --> 00:20:02.160 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA gasps]

00:20:02.243 --> 00:20:03.661 position:50% align:center
Mr. Tanuki?

00:20:05.372 --> 00:20:08.249 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA] What do I do?
What do I do? What do I do?

00:20:10.168 --> 00:20:11.378 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA]
Just focus!

00:20:11.461 --> 00:20:14.089 position:50% align:center
But I'm so scared,
I can't even think straight.

00:20:14.172 --> 00:20:15.382 position:50% align:center
Watch yourself!

00:20:19.761 --> 00:20:21.179 position:50% align:center
He's eating you!

00:20:21.262 --> 00:20:24.307 position:50% align:center
I don't mind. I can regenerate
my body, remember?

00:20:24.391 --> 00:20:26.601 position:50% align:center
You wouldn't have to
if I was stronger.

00:20:27.727 --> 00:20:29.104 position:50% align:center
[FROG KEMONO J growls]

00:20:29.187 --> 00:20:31.773 position:50% align:center
I've always been
such a weakling.

00:20:31.856 --> 00:20:34.859 position:50% align:center
[YUI] Akira. I don't want
you to waste your energy.

00:20:34.943 --> 00:20:38.113 position:50% align:center
I know that I'm strong,
and you never have been.

00:20:38.196 --> 00:20:40.407 position:50% align:center
Let the strong ones take
care of all the scary,

00:20:40.490 --> 00:20:41.866 position:50% align:center
painful stuff, okay?

00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:44.160 position:50% align:center
I'll make sure that you'll
never have to do a thing.

00:20:44.244 --> 00:20:46.746 position:50% align:center
I don't want to live
like that anymore.

00:20:46.830 --> 00:20:48.873 position:50% align:center
Kabane is my friend!

00:20:48.957 --> 00:20:51.543 position:50% align:center
I want... I want...

00:20:51.626 --> 00:20:54.587 position:50% align:center
I want to be useful, too!

00:21:09.394 --> 00:21:12.272 position:50% align:center
Wait. Is this stuff ice?

00:21:12.355 --> 00:21:14.566 position:50% align:center
Did I do all of this?

00:21:14.649 --> 00:21:16.192 position:50% align:center
[KABANE]
Akira.

00:21:16.276 --> 00:21:18.862 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA gasps]
I'm sorry, Kabane!

00:21:18.945 --> 00:21:20.321 position:50% align:center
This is all my fault.

00:21:20.405 --> 00:21:21.489 position:50% align:center
You did great.

00:21:21.573 --> 00:21:22.866 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA]
Huh?

00:21:22.949 --> 00:21:24.951 position:50% align:center
Ya got every last one of 'em.

00:21:25.035 --> 00:21:27.620 position:50% align:center
[gasps, chuckles]

00:21:27.704 --> 00:21:29.205 position:50% align:center
Yup!

00:21:29.289 --> 00:21:31.750 position:50% align:center
Oh, hold on, Kabane.
We have to take a selfie!

00:21:31.833 --> 00:21:32.959 position:50% align:center
[KABANE]
Selfie?

00:21:33.043 --> 00:21:35.086 position:50% align:center
[AKIRA] Yeah! To commemorate
me going for it!

00:21:35.170 --> 00:21:37.922 position:50% align:center
I mean, Shiki is never
going to believe this.

00:21:38.006 --> 00:21:41.051 position:50% align:center
Okay, here's the camera.
Look this way!

00:21:42.469 --> 00:21:44.637 position:50% align:center
Hello, kemonoist.

00:21:44.721 --> 00:21:48.016 position:50% align:center
Apologies for the thankless job.

00:21:48.099 --> 00:21:52.520 position:50% align:center
My former kin were devouring
not only humans,

00:21:52.604 --> 00:21:56.232 position:50% align:center
but their own young
and eggs, as well.

00:21:56.316 --> 00:22:00.070 position:50% align:center
Now their souls
may rest in peace.

00:22:00.153 --> 00:22:02.906 position:50% align:center
Thank you for that, friend.

00:22:02.989 --> 00:22:04.741 position:50% align:center
I'll be back again soon.

00:22:04.824 --> 00:22:07.243 position:50% align:center
You may need a hand
with burying the dead.

00:22:07.327 --> 00:22:10.163 position:50% align:center
[ELDER FROG KEMONO chuckles]

00:22:10.246 --> 00:22:13.958 position:50% align:center
Okiedokes, here goes!
Gimme a big ol' smile!

00:22:16.378 --> 00:22:21.383 position:50% align:center
